    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid value for someone seeking a reliable daily driver. The engine and transmission are functioning well, providing consistent performance on the road. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and some minor dings on the body panels. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining from regular use. While it is mechanically sound for everyday commuting, it may require some minor cosmetic attention and routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in top shape.",
